# Quality Gates

Before considering code changes complete, verify the packages you touched:

```bash
pnpm --filter @nova/shared build   # if shared types/schemas changed
pnpm --filter @nova/api db:generate  # if Prisma schema changed
pnpm --filter @nova/api typecheck
pnpm --filter @nova/dashboard typecheck
```

For broader changes, prefer:

```bash
pnpm typecheck
pnpm lint
```

## Rules

- Do **not** skip gates, use `--no-verify`, or disable rules to land broken code.
- Fix type errors you introduce; do not paper over with `any` or `@ts-ignore`.
- Pre-commit (Husky) runs `lint-staged` (ESLint + Prettier). Keep that green; do not weaken `.husky/pre-commit`.
- If `tsc` hangs on `@nova/ai`, typecheck API/dashboard packages directly rather than abandoning checks.

## After fixes

Re-run the relevant typecheck until it exits 0. Note only real blockers (missing env, external services).
